                    <span>"Guns and Roses" is one of the best books I have seen on the subject of Chicago gangster history. Meticulously researched and beautifully written, it was a pleasure to read and I have no problem recommending it to anyone looking for information on non-Capone gangsters. This Chicagoan is pleased!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Is it fact or fiction?</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
